Retorik.
Værket er en forkortet udgave af Timār al-qulūb fī mudāf wal-mansūb af 'Abd al-Malik ibn Muhammad al-Ta'ālibi (d. 429 H [1038]) og ordnet alfabetisk.
Købt i Kairo 1763 af den danske filolog F. C. von Haven (d. 1763).
Cod. Arab. 206

Rhetoric.
The text is an abridgement of Timār al-qulūb fī mudāf wal-mansūb written by 'Abd al-Malik ibn Muhammad al-Ta'ālibi (d. 429 H [1038 CE])and alphabetical arranged.
Bought in Cairo in 1763 by the Danish phologist F. C. von Hanven (d. 1763).
